rlm-sandbox-bq-rm

Multi-select BigQuery tables from the sandbox project/datasets via fzf
and permanently delete the selected tables. Lists tables restricted to
the datasets defined in $SANDBOX_BQ_DATASETS. Shares the table-list
cache with rlm-sandbox-bq-open (~/.cache/sandbox-bq-open/items.txt).

After confirming selection, prompts for confirmation before deleting.
On success, invalidates the item cache so the next run reflects current
state. Press Ctrl-P to cycle the preview pane height.

ENVIRONMENT
  SANDBOX_BQ_PROJECT   GCP project ID (required).
  SANDBOX_BQ_DATASETS  Colon-separated list of dataset names (required).

REQUIRES
  bq, fzf, jq
